%% ML Metadata - Data Flow Diagram
%% Generated by: Claude Opus 4.6

sequenceDiagram
    participant DSP as Data Science Pipeline<br/>(Driver/Executor)
    participant KFUI as Kubeflow Pipelines UI
    participant MLMD as MLMD gRPC Server<br/>8080/TCP gRPC/HTTP2
    participant DB as MySQL/PostgreSQL<br/>3306/5432 TCP

    Note over DSP,DB: Flow 1: Pipeline Run Metadata Recording

    DSP->>MLMD: PutExecutionType<br/>gRPC/HTTP2<br/>Optional TLS/mTLS
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE execution_type<br/>DB Protocol<br/>Optional TLS
    DB-->>MLMD: OK
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutExecutionTypeResponse

    DSP->>MLMD: PutExecution<br/>(execution + artifacts + events + contexts)<br/>Atomic operation
    MLMD->>DB: BEGIN TRANSACTION<br/>INSERT execution, artifacts, events
    DB-->>MLMD: COMMIT OK
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutExecutionResponse

    DSP->>MLMD: PutArtifacts<br/>(output datasets, models, metrics)
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE artifacts
    DB-->>MLMD: OK
    MLMD-->>DSP: PutArtifactsResponse

    DSP->>MLMD: PutContexts + PutAttributionsAndAssociations<br/>(link to pipeline/experiment context)
    MLMD->>DB: INSERT contexts, attributions, associations
    DB-->>MLMD: OK
    MLMD-->>DSP: OK

    Note over KFUI,DB: Flow 2: Lineage Query

    KFUI->>MLMD: GetExecutionsByContext<br/>(pipeline run context)<br/>gRPC/HTTP2
    MLMD->>DB: SELECT executions WHERE context_id=...<br/>DB Protocol
    DB-->>MLMD: Result set
    MLMD-->>KFUI: GetExecutionsByContextResponse

    KFUI->>MLMD: GetLineageSubgraph<br/>(artifact/execution lineage traversal)
    MLMD->>DB: Recursive lineage query
    DB-->>MLMD: Lineage graph data
    MLMD-->>KFUI: GetLineageSubgraphResponse
